A ARM M0 based on SAMD chip version of the Arduino zero driving a stepper motor
Hardware for the Arduino Nano Stepper board: 
https://github.com/Misfittech/nano_stepper/blob/master/hardware/Nano%20Zero%20R1.0.pdf
Firmware for the bootloader:
https://github.com/Misfittech/ArduinoCore-samd/tree/master/bootloaders/nano_zero
